The Make Utility [5 pts]

In a one page report, briefly address each of the following items:

    Describe the purpose of the make utility
    Explain in your own words how the make utility works
    Discuss the benefits of using the make utility
    Create and submit a working makefile for your homework 1 submission

We may briefly discuss this topic in class but you're responsible for doing the majority of reserach on your own. Fortunately, there is a lot of information available on the internet about this utility. 
